OL,3,C'Care watchdog must do better': New
OL,4,Claw urged to protect residents from
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FThe UK's care homes watchdog must "do
OL,8,Fits job better" in order to protect
OL,9,Fresidents, the leader of the Liberal
OL,10,FDemocrats has said in an emotional
OL,11,Fplea.
OL,13,FSir Ed Davey hit out at the Care
OL,14,FQuality Commission (CQC) while
OL,15,Fspeaking on ITV's This Morning
OL,16,Fprogramme as part of a campaign to
OL,17,Fcreate a new law, which was launched
OL,18,Fafter ITV News uncovered shocking
OL,19,Fstatistics about abuse and neglect in
OL,20,Fcare homes.
