OL,3,C'Care watchdog must do better': New
OL,4,Claw urged to protect residents from
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FThe LibDems leader was speaking
OL,8,Falongside campaigner Clare Miller, who
OL,9,Fwants the government to bring in
OL,10,F"Ann's Law" after her mother who was
OL,11,Fabused in a care home.
OL,13,FAnn's Law would create a register for
OL,14,Fcarers, from which bad staff could be
OL,15,Fstruck off, and make the abuse or
OL,16,Fneglect of care home residents a
OL,17,Fspecific offence.
