OL,3,C'Care watchdog must do better': New
OL,4,Claw urged to protect residents from
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FViewers of This Morning fought back
OL,8,Ftears on Thursday after watching
OL,9,Ffootage, gathered via a hidden camera,
OL,10,Fwhich uncovered shocking evidence of
OL,11,F88-year-old dementia patient Ann King
OL,12,Fbeing abused.
OL,14,FThe upsetting images appeared to show
OL,15,FAnn being mocked, teased and
OL,16,Fmanhandled at the Reigate Grange care
OL,17,Fhome in Surrey, which she was paying
OL,18,F#8,000 a month to look after her.
