OL,3,C'Care watchdog must do better': New
OL,4,Claw urged to protect residents from
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FClare's brother Richard installed the
OL,8,Fhidden camera after noticing their mum
OL,9,Fappeared to be "absolutely terrified"
OL,10,Fby her carers and what they eventually
OL,11,Fsaw shocked them.
OL,13,F"It broke my heart, I will never
OL,14,Fforget it," she told This Morning.
OL,16,FDespite the horrific evidence, no one
OL,17,Fwas ever changed with a crime. An ITV
OL,18,FNews investigation in 2023 found just
OL,19,F1.4% of allegations of neglect and
OL,20,Fabuse at care homes result is someone
OL,21,Fbeing charged with a crime.
