OL,7,FAfter discovering how widespread the
OL,8,Fproblem is, Clare - herself a carer of
OL,9,F27 years - teamed up with Sir Ed to
OL,10,Fcampaign for the safety of care home
OL,11,Fresidents.
OL,13,FWhat happened to care home resident
OL,14,FAnn King?
