OL,3,C'Care watchdog must do better': New
OL,4,Claw urged to protect residents from
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FThe MP, who is a carer for his young
OL,8,Fdisabled son, said: "I couldn't be
OL,9,Fmore committed to improving the
OL,10,Fquality of care for the whole of our
OL,11,Fcountry and for the millions of others
OL,12,Fwho are like me, who have their loved
OL,13,Fones in the care homes."
OL,15,FHe said the CQC isn't getting to the
OL,16,Fheart of the challenges within care
OL,17,Fhomes or addressing the issues fast
OL,18,Fenough to make change.
