OL,3,C'Care watchdog must do better': New
OL,4,Claw urged to protect residents from
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"I think it's about getting the Care
OL,8,FQuality Commission in the right place,
OL,9,Fand hopefully the new head Julian
OL,10,FHartley will do that, but also it's
OL,11,Fabout making sure we improve the
OL,12,Fquality of carers to make sure that
OL,13,Fall of them are really good, and we
OL,14,Froot out the bad apples."
OL,16,FHe added: "We need Care Quality
OL,17,FCommission to do its job better."
