OL,3,C'Care watchdog must do better': New
OL,4,Claw urged to protect residents from
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FCQC interim Chief Inspector of Adult
OL,8,FSocial Care and Integrated Care James
OL,9,FBullion told ITV News the watchdog is
OL,10,Fcommitted to improving.
OL,12,F"It is essential that when people
OL,13,Fshare concerns with us they're acted
OL,14,Fon appropriately and we will continue
OL,15,Fto push for improvements on how CQC
OL,16,Flistens and acts on this information.
OL,17,FWe are working hard to improve our
OL,18,Fregulatory oversight, including
OL,19,Fincreasing the number of inspections
OL,20,Fwe do to give the public confidence in
OL,21,Fquality of care.
