OL,7,F"Care homes are people's homes and
OL,8,Feveryone living there deserves to be
OL,9,Ftreated with dignity and respect, to
OL,10,Fbe listened to, and to be given safe,
OL,11,Fhigh-quality care and we will continue
OL,12,Fto hold providers to account where we
OL,13,Ffind this is not the case."
OL,15,FIn a statement, Signature Senior
OL,16,FLifestyle, which runs Reigate Grange,
OL,17,Fsaid: "The behaviour of the
OL,18,Findividuals concerned was
OL,19,Freprehensible and fell far short of
OL,20,Fthe standards of care we provide our
OL,21,Fresidents every day.
