OL,7,F"You can go into a care home and look
OL,8,Fafter a vulnerable person, someone
OL,9,Fwith disabilities, an adult with
OL,10,Flearning disabilities or an elderly
OL,11,Fperson with dementia and you don't
OL,12,Fhave to have any qualifications or
OL,13,Fyou're not registered... I think
OL,14,Fthat's wrong.
