OL,7,F"We don't pay them enough and we don't
OL,8,Faccredit them enough and we don't make
OL,9,Fsure it's a really well qualified
OL,10,Fprofession, and I think that
OL,11,Fundersells care workers. I think they
OL,12,Fare some of the most amazing people in
OL,13,Four world actually, doing an
OL,14,Fincredibly tough job."
